subject: Printing results from JUnit
msgSnippet: I am using the graphical version of JUnit and was wondering if it is possible to get a hardcopy or file based report on a test run. Obviousy for a successful
messageBody:
I am using the graphical version of JUnit and was wondering
if it is possible to get a hardcopy or file based report on
a test run.

Obviousy for a successful run this is only the number of runs
but for a failure this would be the list of errors.

TIA

Steve
